r / monthFor growing businesses to streamline teamwork. [Get started](https://www.notion.com/signup?target=plans) Everything in Plus, and:Does work for you. Completes complex, multi-step tasks using context from Notion, your connected apps, and the web.Notion AgentAI agents handle repetitive tasks autonomously, so your team doesn芒聙聶t have to. Free to try, then $10 per 1,000 credits.Custom AgentsAutomate your meeting notes and follow-ups, no bot neededAI Meeting NotesSearch across connected apps like Slack, Github & moreEnterprise SearchBetaManage employee access at scale with secure single sign-on.SAML SSOCollaborate in Notion databases without giving access to the entire database. Limit access to rows where the collaborator is assigned.Granular database permissionsAdd a verified badge to pages that are up to date. Appears in search results and AI citations.Verify any pageCreate teamspaces that can芒聙聶t be seen or discovered by anyone except those you add. Great for sensitive information like company planning or performance reviews.Private teamspacesVerify ownership of an email domain to access advanced security features including single-sign on.Domain verificationConnect to GitHub, Asana & morePremium connectionsCustom Agents automate work that repeats.Set them up once, and the entire team benefits. [Learn more 芒聠聮](https://www.notion.com/product/agents) All our teams, docs, and workflows are in Notion, and it芒聙聶s listening to Slack. When your agents have full context across the company, that芒聙聶s what makes them useful.Morgane PalomaresVP of Marketing, BraintrustYour Notion Agent can build, edit, and take action.Anything you can do in Notion, your Notion Agent can do for you. [Learn more 芒聠聮](https://www.notion.com/product/agents) Enterprise Search finds answers across all your apps.Search across Slack, Google Drive, GitHub & more芒聙聰in seconds. [Learn more 芒聠聮](https://www.notion.com/product/enterprise-search) AI Meeting Notes gives your team perfect meeting memory.Capture every detail and actionable summaries, right where you work. [Learn more 芒聠聮](https://www.notion.com/product/ai-meeting-notes) Designed for teams.Usage & analytics dashboardsTrack Notion credit usage, view detailed analytics and ROI insights.Custom permissionsYou芒聙聶re in control of what Notion AI can see and do.Model agnosticSwitch any workflow to a different model or provider, without losing any context.Governance tools & controlsGet a bird芒聙聶s eye view of AI actions across your workspace, with controls for who can do what.Trusted by enterprise. [Learn more about security practices 芒聠聮](https://www.notion.so/help/notion-ai-security-practices?_gl=1*p1njrn*_gcl_au*MTcxMjUyNjE2LjE3NDQ4MTY4MzM.*_ga*MTgyNjkyNzg0MS4xNzI5MTA5MzMx*_ga_9ZJ8CB186L*MTc0NjA0NDM5Mi4yMzcuMS4xNzQ2MDQ1Njk5LjUwLjAuMA..) No training on your dataWe have contractual agreements with our AI subprocessors that prohibit the use of customer data to train their models.SOC 2 Type 2 & ISO 27001Notion is committed to the highest requirements of information security.GDPR & CCPAWe have mapped our privacy program to the GDPR and other global privacy regulations.Secure encryptionWhen you use Notion AI, your data is encrypted in-transit using TLS 1.2 or greater.Zero data retention for EnterpriseNo data is stored with LLM providers. 30 day retention for non-Enterprise. [Contact sales芒聠聮](https://www.notion.com/contact-sales) HIPAA compliant for EnterpriseNotion AI enables HIPAA compliance by utilizing LLM provider芒聙聶s zero-retention APIs and allows for the processing of protected health information (PHI). [Contact sales芒聠聮](https://www.notion.com/contact-sales) See what Notion AI can do. [Explore all use cases 芒聠聮](https://www.notion.com/product/ai/use-cases) Onboard a new hire 芒聠聮 Go from brainstorm to roadmap 芒聠聮 Automate weekly reporting 芒聠聮 Triage product feedback 芒聠聮 Resolve support tickets in Slack 芒聠聮 Respond to security alerts faster 芒聠聮 Questions & answersWhat can Notion AI help me do?Notion AI is your built-in teammate inside Notion, working directly in your pages, docs, tasks, and databases so you can move faster without switching tools. Using context from your workspace and connected apps (when enabled), it helps you turn ideas into finished work all in one place.Here芒聙聶s what you can do with Notion AI:Chat with [Notion Agent](https://www.notion.com/help/notion-ai-faqs#personal-agent) to take on entire tasks, using context from your workspace and connected apps to create and edit pages and databases.Use [Custom Agents](https://www.notion.com/help/custom-agent) to automate recurring work for your team, like answering questions on Slack, routing tasks, and sharing project updates .Search across your workspace and connected apps like Slack and Google Drive with [Enterprise Search](https://www.notion.com/help/notion-ai-faqs#enterprise-search) and [Notion AI Connectors](https://www.notion.com/help/notion-ai-connectors) ,, so you can find answers without jumping between tools.Capture meetings with [AI Meeting Notes](https://www.notion.com/help/notion-ai-faqs#ai-meeting-notes-(beta)) , which transcribe conversations, summarize key points, and surface insights automatically.Dive deep on a topic with [Research Mode](https://www.notion.com/help/notion-ai-faqs#research-mode) to generate detailed reports and summaries.Improve writing or generate drafts with [AI blocks](https://www.notion.com/help/notion-ai-faqs#notion-ai-inline) directly in your pages.Create [databases](https://www.notion.com/help/notion-ai-faqs#notion-ai-for-databases) , auto-populate properties with [Autofill](https://www.notion.com/help/autofill#autofill) , and write formulas for smarter workflows and automations.To ensure optimal performance and fair use across all Notion AI users, your access to AI features can be temporarily reduced depending on your usage.What are Custom Agents?Custom Agents automate recurring work for your entire team. Set a trigger or schedule, and the agent handles it from there芒聙聰24/7, whether you're online or not. One person builds it, and the whole team benefits. [Learn more.](https://www.notion.com/help/custom-agent) How does Notion AI use my data?We follow our standard [data protection practices](https://www.notion.com/security) to keep your data encrypted and private. Notion AI will not use your data to train our models unless you opt in to a request to share your data.Any information used to power Notion AI will be shared with AI subprocessors for the sole purpose of providing you with the Notion AI features. We specifically have contractual agreements in place with our AI subprocessors that prohibit the use of customer data to train their models. [Learn more about Notion AI security and privacy practices here.](https://www.notion.com/help/notion-ai-security-practices) How much does Notion AI cost? (and what are Notion credits)?Notion AI is included with Notion芒聙聶s Business and Enterprise plans, with core features like Notion Agent, AI Meeting Notes, and Enterprise Search. Workspaces on other plans get a limited amount of trial usage to try it out.Why are Custom Agents priced differently?Custom Agents can run on schedules or triggers and complete multi-step work across your workspace and connected tools. Admins can purchase Notion credits as an add-on for Business and Enterprise plans. Notion credits let teams scale that usage up or down based on how much automation they run. [Learn more](https://www.notion.com/help/custom-agent-pricing) .What are Notion credits?Custom Agents run on Notion credits. Notion credits are available as an add-on to Business and Enterprise plans for teams that need always-on automation. Each run uses credits based on how much work the agent does, and admins can track usage in the Notion credits dashboard. [Learn more](https://www.notion.com/help/notion-credits-dashboard) .When do Notion credits go into effect?Now through May 3, 2026:Custom Agents are free to use on Business and Enterprise plans, including Business trials. During this time, teams can explore how Custom Agents fit into their workflows, and admins can track their team's patterns in the [Notion credits dashboard](https://www.notion.com/help/notion-credits-dashboard) to understand usage and estimate future credit needs.Admins (Business and Enterprise plans) can manage who can create Custom Agents and disable Agents anytime to guide controlled rollouts.Starting May 4, 2026:Custom Agents will start using Notion credits when they run. Admins can purchase additional credits, and if credits are insufficient, agents will automatically pause until more are added.How can I learn more about Notion AI?Visit our [Help Center](https://www.notion.com/help/notion-ai-faqs) and [Notion Academy](https://academy.notion.com/?from=marketing&pathname=%2Fproduct%2Fai&tid=323f2fae1b4445c2ac65319545bb3224) for guides, examples, and best practices for using Notion AI and Custom Agents.","snippet":"Meet your 24/7 AI teamInfinite minds, built for teamwork. Answer questions, prioritize tasks, and write reports芒聙聰all while you sleep. [Try for free](https://www.notion.com/signup?from=marketing&pathname=%2Fproduct%2Fai&tid=323f2fae1b4445c2ac65319545bb3224) [Request a demo](https://www.notion.com/contact-sales) Trusted by teams atAgentsEnterprise searchAI Meeting NotesAdmin controlsEnterprise Search 16:10Admin Controls 16:10If it芒聙聶s something that芒聙聶s repetitive, we have a Notion Agent for it.Ben Lev...","metadata":"{\"collector\":\"playwright; fallbackReason=HTTP collect failed: Remote host terminated the handshake\",\"sourceUrls\":[],\"qualitySignals\":[\"MAIN_CONTENT_READY\",\"NO_STRUCTURED_BLOCKS\"],\"qualityScore\":0.52,\"structuredBlocks\":[],\"collectedAt\":\"2026-06-20T06:18:16.378861100Z\",\"durationMillis\":24571}","competitorName":"Notion AI","sourceType":"OFFICIAL","collectedAt":"2026-06-20T06:18:16.378861100Z","success":true,"errorMessage":null}}],"selectedTargets":[{"candidate":{"url":"https://notion.so/product/ai","ti