 contains all the project info to not just plan the thing, but build the thing.We can see a project's going to have three sprints, we can see all the tasks for those sprints, and everything's linked in the roadmap.Joy TaoCo-founder and CTO, PartifulConnections with GitHub, Slack, & more bring all your work togetherFigmaAlways share the most updated designs with your team. [Try now芒聠聮](https://www.notion.com/integrations/figma) SlackSimply paste a link to see the full message without switching tools. [Try now芒聠聮](https://www.notion.com/integrations/slack) GitHubBring pull requests, issues, and even repos directly into Notion. [Try now芒聠聮](https://www.notion.com/integrations/github) AmplitudeTrack release metrics, experiment results, and more. [Try now芒聠聮](https://www.notion.com/integrations/amplitude) JiraSee bug updates, or convert an entire project into a database. [Try now芒聠聮](https://www.notion.com/integrations/jira) Browse all connections [Go to the gallery芒聠聮](https://www.notion.com/integrations) Top teams run projects with NotionRated best on G2Notion consistently ranks as the G2 industry leader based on hundreds of customer reviews. But don't take our word for it. Check out G2's reviews for more info. [Get started芒聠聮](https://www.notion.com/signup?from=marketing&pathname=%2Fproduct%2Fprojects&tid=3d3b4983ab1341baa06eb87efa7a63d6) 芒聙聹Collaboration is not something you set and forget. It芒聙聶s a muscle you have to keep flexing. Choosing a tool like Notion makes that easier and more enjoyable for everyone.芒聙聺Ricky RamsaranWeb Experiences Program Manager, FigmaHaving a single hub for every project has become our source of truth and eliminates the confusion of scattered information across multiple toolsAds DawsonStaff Engineer, CohereThe best part about Notion for a growing company is that it doesn芒聙聶t lock you into a rigid one-size-fits-all system. Instead, you can adapt and iterate a custom-built solution for your teams as you grow.Brian EmerickTechnical Program M