e as businessAutomatically create pages and new blocks, set status, assignee, and property values, and more.AutomationsBasicbuttons onlyCustomdatabase automationsSame as plusSame as plusSee up-to-date information from Jira, GitHub & Asana, all synced into Notion as a database.1-way database syncsSame as businessWeb publishingPublish an unlimited number of pages to the web.Unlimited published pagesSelect a custom notion.site domain for your published pages.notion.site domains1555Turn on search engine indexing for any Site. Upgrade to a paid plan to customize your title and description metadata.Search engine indexing (SEO)BasicAdvancedAdvancedAdvancedSet a homepage, customize your Site芒聙聶s favicon and share preview, build a custom header bar, and set light or dark mode.Site customizationsConnect a custom domain to your Site and remove Notion branding for $8/month/domain paid annually, or $10/month per domain paid monthly.Custom domains and brandingPay per domainPay per domainPay per domainAdmin & securityCreate a backup of all the pages and content across your workspace.Export entire workspace as HTML, Markdown, & CSVEnable an extra layer of account security with a second method of verification, also known as 2FA or MFA.2-step verificationExport all your content at once as PDFs. Perfect for legal or compliance backups.Export entire workspace as PDFManage employee access at scale with secure single sign-on.SAML single sign-on (SSO)Automatically provision members in and out of your workspace with identity providers like Okta.User provisioning (SCIM)Unlock extra permission controls to prevent certain people from sharing pages externally, disable guests, and set workspace-level rules.Advanced workspace & teamspace security controlsOrganization level controlsOrganization level controlsGet actionable insights about how folks use your Notion workspace, from the most popular pages to overall traffic. Analytics data begins after Enterprise Plan start date.Workspace analyticsDe