 you offer student discounts?The Plus Plan (with a 1-member limit) is free for students and educators. Compared to the Free Plan, you芒聙聶ll be able to add more guests,\",\"snippet\":\"ver the block storage limit on a Free Plan?If you芒聙聶re using a Free Plan workspace by yourself, you芒聙聶ll be able to add as many pages and blocks as you like.If you芒聙聶re using a Free Plan\",\"sourceUrls\":[\"https://notion.so/pricing\"],\"issueFlags\":[],\"createdAt\":[2026,6,20,14,20,11,995619400]},{\"id\":9352,\"taskId\":50,\"knowledgeDocumentId\":50,\"competitorName\":\"Notion AI\",\"evidenceId\":\"T0050-COLLECT_SOURCES_01_03-001\",\"documentKey\":\"TASK-50-T0050-COLLECT-SOURCES-01-03-001\",\"retrievalScope\":\"TASK\",\"scopeRefKey\":\"50\",\"knowledgeDomainKey\":null,\"chunkKey\":\"TASK-50-T0050-COLLECT-SOURCES-01-03-001#CHUNK-031\",\"chunkIndex\":30,\"startOffset\":15707,\"endOffset\":16307,\"sourceCategory\":\"AI_DISCOVERED\",\"documentVersion\":1,\"content\":\"nts and educators. Compared to the Free Plan, you芒聙聶ll be able to add more guests, have access to more version history, and upload larger files.Just sign up with your school email address and you芒聙聶ll immediately gain access to these features. Thousands of school email domains are eligible, not just .edu!For more info & FAQs, [visit the Notion for Education page](https://www.notion.so/help/notion-for-education) .What do the different analytics tiers mean?Basic page analytics (Free and Plus Plans): Includes a list of page viewers as well as a chart displaying views over time.Advanced page analytics\",\"snippet\":\"nts and educators. Compared to the Free Plan, you芒聙聶ll be able to add more guests, have access to more version history, and upload larger files.Just sign up with your school email ad\",\"sourceUrls\":[\"https://notion.so/pricing\"],\"issueFlags\":[],\"createdAt\":[2026,6,20,14,20,11,997585300]},{\"id\":9353,\"taskId\":50,\"knowledgeDocumentId\":50,\"competitorName\":\"Notion AI\",\"evidenceId\":\"T0050-COLLECT_SOURC