n selecting Billing, then Change plan. After you cancel, you芒聙聶ll still have access to all the paid features until the end of your billing cycle.Learn more about billing in [this article](https://www.notion.com/help/billing)\",\"snippet\":\"ll be downgraded at the end of your billing cycle. Learn about how your features may be impacted after a downgrade [here 芒聠聮](https://notion.com/help/plan-downgrade) How do I cancel \",\"sourceUrls\":[\"https://notion.so/pricing\"],\"issueFlags\":[],\"createdAt\":[2026,6,20,14,20,12,9716000]},{\"id\":9360,\"taskId\":50,\"knowledgeDocumentId\":50,\"competitorName\":\"Notion AI\",\"evidenceId\":\"T0050-COLLECT_SOURCES_01_03-001\",\"documentKey\":\"TASK-50-T0050-COLLECT-SOURCES-01-03-001\",\"retrievalScope\":\"TASK\",\"scopeRefKey\":\"50\",\"knowledgeDomainKey\":null,\"chunkKey\":\"TASK-50-T0050-COLLECT-SOURCES-01-03-001#CHUNK-039\",\"chunkIndex\":38,\"startOffset\":19900,\"endOffset\":20503,\"sourceCategory\":\"AI_DISCOVERED\",\"documentVersion\":1,\"content\":\".Learn more about billing in [this article](https://www.notion.com/help/billing) .What happens if my payment fails? Like if my credit card expires?Your account email will be notified after each failed payment. Payments may be retried up to 8 times within the next month. After this, if the payment did not succeed, your workspace will get restricted to limited-access for a period of time before being downgraded to the Free plan.Can I change my payment method?You can change your payment method at any time in your billing settings.How do refunds work?Our refund policy is simple. If you believe you've\",\"snippet\":\".Learn more about billing in [this article](https://www.notion.com/help/billing) .What happens if my payment fails? Like if my credit card expires?Your account email will be notifi\",\"sourceUrls\":[\"https://notion.so/pricing\"],\"issueFlags\":[],\"createdAt\":[2026,6,20,14,20,12,11431500]},{\"id\":9361,\"taskId\":50,\"knowledgeDocumentId\":50,\"competitorName\":\"