 workspace where enterprise teams plan, collaborate, and build faster together. [Request a demo](https://www.notion.com/contact-sales) Trusted by 98% of the Forbes Cloud 100Company knowledgeOne home that芒聙聶s organized, searchable, and accurate.Enterprise searchInstantly surface answers across Notion and connected apps.Integrated projectsPlan tasks, track progress, and align teams.Workflows & connectionsAutomate any process and integrate your tools.wip-aifw-company-homeEnterprise Search#1knowledge base and AI writing assistant (G2)98%of Forbes Cloud 100 teams use Notion62%of Fortune 100 companies use NotionAll-in-one AI, right where you work.AI with all the right contextNot just another generic AI tool芒聙聰it芒聙聶s AI powered by your team芒聙聶s knowledge and workflows.One AI tool for everythingBrainstorm, write, code, search, and automate workflows, all in Notion. No need for multiple AI point solutions.Fully integrated in your daily workNo app jumping or context-switching芒聙聰access AI directly where you plan, build, track, and collaborate.Powerful and secureEnterprise-level AI governance, security, and admin controls with zero data retention or training on your data.EmpoweringEasy to start, delightful to use.Designed to feel powerful yet intuitive, Notion is a workspace teams actually want to use.CustomizableFlexible design that grows with you.A customizable workspace that adapts and scales with your team芒聙聶s needs, reducing the need for point solutions, more tool sprawl, and extra costs.ConnectedEvery team on the same page, always.All your tools, teams, and work in an organized, AI-searchable workspace芒聙聰so teams stay aligned, move faster, and make better decisions. [Discover customer stories芒聠聮](https://www.notion.com/customers) Loved by the most innovative teams. [Discover customer stories](https://www.notion.com/customers) Notion芒聙聶s ease of use is one of its hallmarks. It helps you visually navigate content and remember where something is.Marie SzutsHead of People Ops, FigmaNotion is saving new employees days, if not weeks, of their onboarding to be able to find information and quickly learn from it.Scott EntwistleSenior Recruiter, RemoteNotion has been the most powerful and impactful way to streamline our workflow.Rahim MakaniDirector of Product, MatchNot only do our streamlined workflows in Notion save us time, they also make it easier to stay up to date on task details and progress.Taku WakasugiResearch, ToyotaNotion AI removes administrative tasks that often plague product teams, keeping them focused on what they're best at芒聙聰building great products.Geoff CharlesCPO, RampWhat used to take hours of debugging can now be solved in minutes just by asking Notion AI.John AllardEngineering, OpenAISimplify your product development.Build better products faster by streamlining your entire development process in one connected hub. [Learn more芒聠聮](https://www.notion.com/product/notion-for-product-development) If the most creative people spent a little less time on ideas and a little more on organizing the ideas they've already got, they would make more of an impact. And that's where Notion comes in.Scott BelskyChief Product Officer, AdobeConnectionsConnect all your essential tools.Bring all your tools together in one place. Integrate, sync, and automate workflows, embed rich information, and find answers across your apps. [See all integrations芒聠聮](https://www.notion.com/integrations) Build boldly with best-in-class support and security.Professional servicesDesign, deploy, and automate your Notion workspace at scale with professional expertise.Dedicated guidanceCustomer Success partners with you through workspace setup, onboarding, and best practices.Premium supportTailored, proactive around-the-clock support offerings for teams with more specialized needs.Identity managementSAML-based SSO integration for secure employee access.SCIM user provisioningEasily create, remove, update, or retrieve any user or group.Workspace and domain managem