tion.com/templates/branchs-engineering-roadmap) Mixpanel's daily standup & tasks [Try now芒聠聮](https://www.notion.com/templates/mixpanels-daily-standup-and-tasks) Notion's editorial calendar [Try now芒聠聮](https://www.notion.com/integrations/slack) Wikis and docs included, for the same priceWikisIt芒聙聶s hard to move fast with a clunky & disorganized workspace. Centralize all your knowledge in Notion instead. [Learn more芒聠聮](https://www.notion.com/product/wikis) DocsSimple. Powerful. Beautiful. Communicate more efficiently with flexible building blocks. [Learn more芒聠聮](https://www.notion.com/product/docs) Notion AIAccess the limitless power of AI, right inside Notion. Work faster. Write better. Think bigger. [Learn more芒聠聮](https://www.notion.com/product/ai) Get your projects organizedPlay around with it first. Pay and add your team later. [Get Notion free](https://www.notion.com/signup?from=marketing&pathname=%2Fproduct%2Fprojects&tid=3d3b4983ab1341baa06eb87efa7a63d6) [Request a demo](https://www.notion.com/contact-sales)\\\",\\\"sourceUrls\\\":[\\\"https://notion.so/plans\\\"],\\\"issueFlags\\\":[],\\\"documentVersion\\\":1,\\\"status\\\":\\\"READY\\\",\\\"failureReason\\\":null,\\\"collectedAt\\\":[2026,6,20,14,20,12,50082400],\\\"createdAt\\\":[2026,6,20,14,20,12,57959100],\\\"updatedAt\\\":[2026,6,20,14,20,12,93395000]},\\\"retrievalChunks\\\":[{\\\"id\\\":9365,\\\"taskId\\\":50,\\\"knowledgeDocumentId\\\":51,\\\"competitorName\\\":\\\"Notion AI\\\",\\\"evidenceId\\\":\\\"T0050-COLLECT_SOURCES_01_03-002\\\",\\\"documentKey\\\":\\\"TASK-50-T0050-COLLECT-SOURCES-01-03-002\\\",\\\"retrievalScope\\\":\\\"TASK\\\",\\\"scopeRefKey\\\":\\\"50\\\",\\\"knowledgeDomainKey\\\":null,\\\"chunkKey\\\":\\\"TASK-50-T0050-COLLECT-SOURCES-01-03-002#CHUNK-001\\\",\\\"chunkIndex\\\":0,\\\"startOffset\\\":0,\\\"endOffset\\\":606,\\\"sourceCategory\\\":\\\"AI_DISCOVERED\\\",\\\"documentVersion\\\":1,\\\"content\\\":\\\"ProjectsManage projects from beginning to endWith Notion芒聙聶s connecte