ctivity) Your centralized product development hub in Notion [Read guide芒聠聮](https://www.notion.com/help/guides/your-centralized-product-development-hub-in-notion) Take a self-guided demo of a Notion workspace. [Take a tour芒聠聮](https://demo.hellonotion.com/cm176h6en000003lc8pd81qed?g=cm178nsbp000003l1h9sv1als&s=0) One AI workspace, tailored to every team.Connect with an expert to explore what's possible with Notion. [Request a demo](https://www.notion.com/contact-sales)\\\",\\\"sourceUrls\\\":[\\\"https://notion.so/enterprise\\\"],\\\"issueFlags\\\":[],\\\"documentVersion\\\":1,\\\"status\\\":\\\"READY\\\",\\\"failureReason\\\":null,\\\"collectedAt\\\":[2026,6,20,14,20,12,133820500],\\\"createdAt\\\":[2026,6,20,14,20,12,140722600],\\\"updatedAt\\\":[2026,6,20,14,20,12,166749500]},\\\"retrievalChunks\\\":[{\\\"id\\\":9378,\\\"taskId\\\":50,\\\"knowledgeDocumentId\\\":52,\\\"competitorName\\\":\\\"Notion AI\\\",\\\"evidenceId\\\":\\\"T0050-COLLECT_SOURCES_01_03-003\\\",\\\"documentKey\\\":\\\"TASK-50-T0050-COLLECT-SOURCES-01-03-003\\\",\\\"retrievalScope\\\":\\\"TASK\\\",\\\"scopeRefKey\\\":\\\"50\\\",\\\"knowledgeDomainKey\\\":null,\\\"chunkKey\\\":\\\"TASK-50-T0050-COLLECT-SOURCES-01-03-003#CHUNK-001\\\",\\\"chunkIndex\\\":0,\\\"startOffset\\\":0,\\\"endOffset\\\":603,\\\"sourceCategory\\\":\\\"AI_DISCOVERED\\\",\\\"documentVersion\\\":1,\\\"content\\\":\\\"Notion for EnterpriseKnowledge and work. Connected.One secure AI workspace where enterprise teams plan, collaborate, and build faster together. [Request a demo](https://www.notion.com/contact-sales) Trusted by 98% of the Forbes Cloud 100Company knowledgeOne home that芒聙聶s organized, searchable, and accurate.Enterprise searchInstantly surface answers across Notion and connected apps.Integrated projectsPlan tasks, track progress, and align teams.Workflows & connectionsAutomate any process and integrate your tools.wip-aifw-company-homeEnterprise Search#1knowledge base and AI writing assistant (G2)98%of\\\",\\\"snippet