ms.Workflows & connectionsAutomate any process and integrate your tools.wip-aifw-company-homeEnterprise Search#1knowledge base and AI writing assistant (G2)98%of Forbes Cloud 100 teams use Notion62%of Fortune 100 companies use NotionAll-in-one AI, right where you work.AI with all the right contextNot just another generic AI tool芒聙聰it芒聙聶s AI powered by your team芒聙聶s knowledge and workflows.One AI tool for everythingBrainstorm, write, code, search, and automate workflows, all in Notion. No need for multiple AI point solutions.Fully integrated in your daily workNo app jumping or context-switching芒聙聰access AI directly where you plan, build, track, and collaborate.Powerful and secureEnterprise-level AI governance, security, and admin controls with zero data retention or training on your data.EmpoweringEasy to start, delightful to use.Designed to feel powerful yet intuitive, Notion is a workspace teams actually want to use.CustomizableFlexible design that grows with you.A customizable workspace that adapts and scales with your team芒聙聶s needs, reducing the need for point solutions, more tool sprawl, and extra costs.ConnectedEvery team on the same page, always.All your tools, teams, and work in an organized, AI-searchable workspace芒聙聰so teams stay aligned, move faster, and make better decisions. [Discover customer stories芒聠聮](https://www.notion.com/customers) Loved by the most innovative teams. [Discover customer stories](https://www.notion.com/customers) Notion芒聙聶s ease of use is one of its hallmarks. It helps you visually navigate content and remember where something is.Marie SzutsHead of People Ops, FigmaNotion is saving new employees days, if not weeks, of their onboarding to be able to find information and quickly learn from it.Scott EntwistleSenior Recruiter, RemoteNotion has been the most powerful and impactful way to streamline our workflow.Rahim MakaniDirector of Product, MatchNot only do our streamlined workflows in Notion save us time, they also make it easier to